{"tid":1475121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國曾經倡議將香港設為自由市，不隸屬於任何國家","createTime":"2019-08-15T11:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T11:49:23.000Z","uid":188657,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"446e8d26abfcef7ddc4fb66f638a9d47b1fc563b","tid":1475121,"uid":188657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:18:24.000Z","msg":"第二次世界大戰末期 <br />\n1945年，經歷了香港日佔時期的香港重光。由於香港在被日軍佔領時是英國的殖民地，所以在中、英、美、法、蘇五個列強討論香港戰後地位問題時，美國曾經倡議將香港設為自由市，不隸屬於任何國家，中華民國擁有對香港的主權，但美國和英國可以在香港建立軍事基地。但遭到中華民國和英國的反對，最後英國搶先對香港恢復行使主權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/香港與美國關係\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbgwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=2f560ded\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/香港與美國關係</a>"},{"pid":"d330058c25dbe53d88e90f9ff6efcd65a562ed71","tid":1475121,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:21:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fea6981d32826e8805344245bfa3f76dfb14ccc9","tid":1475121,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:21:37.000Z","msg":"其實係好事嚟"},{"pid":"d84c82fa6584bdfe87f8b21a1cc5e3b618f6f3d0","tid":1475121,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:21:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68716fb31156d05d3064a8c4ff8c3efd0e9dbb60","tid":1475121,"uid":258267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:24:15.000Z","msg":"[緊急呼籲] 818和理非全面進駐維園<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475117</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n818見"},{"pid":"bd9eec113a45a6a95dede6a21f906dcb224cf79b","tid":1475121,"uid":188657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d330058c25dbe53d88e90f9ff6efcd65a562ed71","tid":1475121,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"